				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/D%C4%A9-k%C3%ADnh-t%E1%BA%B7ng-bi%E1%BB%87t/poem-HbgK3vKm_kodDFAsVgQ2Xw">Dĩ kính tặng biệt - 以鏡贈別</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/L%C3%A3o-th%C3%A1i/poem-tvyfaC5bVR1EYeVmjs8jqA">Lão thái - 老態</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%82u-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tu/Phong-L%E1%BA%A1c-%C4%91%C3%ACnh-ti%E1%BB%83u-%E1%BA%A9m/poem-StBCur9DVUdkO1gQLN-nQQ">Phong Lạc đình tiểu ẩm - 丰樂亭小飲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%82u-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tu/author-Rh6zapU4AwLAuhG1Xl_FMw">Âu Dương Tu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ph%E1%BB%A5-t%C3%A2n-h%C3%A0nh/poem-1-ewUEdMXYGTpOMxwIc6Ig">Phụ tân hành - 負薪行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4ng-B%E1%BA%A3n-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/S%C6%A1n-c%C6%B0-b%C3%A1ch-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-k%E1%BB%B3-082/poem-o7X-pwtJRFmXgouutLwfYw">Sơn cư bách vịnh kỳ 082 - 山居百詠其八十二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4ng-B%E1%BA%A3n-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-jnvtlp5PrNS3FoOBBGt7-w">Tông Bản thiền sư</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BA%B7ng-t%C3%AC-b%E1%BB%99-Ti%C3%AAu-lang-trung-th%E1%BA%ADp-huynh/poem-aB57mSvNVwdnkl12M3H0kw">Tặng tì bộ Tiêu lang trung thập huynh - 贈比部蕭郎中十兄</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/Thu-%C6%B0ng/poem-DeUbMVuurIa40MhoXadRJQ">Thu ưng - 秋鷹</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-h%E1%BB%AFu-t%E1%BB%AB-1/poem-H9h3VFpWVHWoW69g54MirA">Tường hữu từ 1 - 墻有茨 1</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-th%C3%ADch-Ng%C3%B4-S%E1%BB%9F-l%C6%B0u-bi%E1%BB%87t-Ch%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-s%E1%BB%A9-qu%C3%A2n-l%C6%B0u-h%E1%BA%ADu-ki%C3%AAm-m%E1%BA%A1c-ph%E1%BB%A7-ch%C6%B0-c%C3%B4ng-%C4%91%E1%BA%AFc-li%E1%BB%85u-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-VusrYuqrkvq24lkjJ2HUYQ">Tương thích Ngô Sở, lưu biệt Chương sứ quân lưu hậu kiêm mạc phủ chư công, đắc liễu tự - 將適吳楚，留別章使君留後兼幕府諸公，得柳字</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%E1%BB%A8c/Xu%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ADt-th%C3%B4n-c%C6%B0/poem-MZ7wtBgui0H8ScHAjUpaNg">Xuân nhật thôn cư - 春日村居</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%E1%BB%A8c/author-KitWPFSrhqgQGR4JMcSBew">Nguyễn Ức</a>)<br></div>	</div>
